Connect to external MCP servers:

  import { connectMCPServers } from '@kitn/mcp-client';
  const mcp = await connectMCPServers(plugin, {
    servers: [{ name: 'github', transport: { type: 'http', url: '...' } }],
  });

MCP tools are registered with namespaced names (e.g. github_createIssue).
See src/ai/mcp-client/client.ts for configuration options.
